<br>
Like he isn't just playing that all the time now...  like that is better then eq?  I have seen people play CS and Team fortress and all those FPS games just as much as I see people playing EQ.  It's the online connection to real people that makes the game exciting.<br>
<br>
My favorite part was when the mother was pointing to the characters on screen.  She was saying &quot;look, those aren't real people, its a game.&quot;   If you think about it..  those are in fact real people.  That is why the game is so social compaired to video games 10 years ago when all those other people were AI from the game.<br>
<br>
That is why when your on a raid your so distracted.  You can't just pause the game.  Those are real people waiting for you to make your next move/pull/heal/whatever.<br>
<br>
It's not that you are a heartless person, but you get a phone call during a raid you of course are distracted.<br>
<br>
In all honesty, I am the same way when I watch TV.  At least with the game I say afk, phone.  and then turn completely away from the game so I can focus on the phone caller.  If I am watching TV when I get a call and its a good show, sorry phone caller, I can't go afk with the TV show.<br>
<br>
